Package de.hsb.ms.syn.common.audio

Abstract AudioAlgorithm classes and its linked resource classes (Scale, Properties) providing the base for the audio processing that takes place in this application.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AudioAlgorithm
    Base class for Delegate algorithms used by both GenNode and FXNode instances It is extended by FXDelegate and GenDelegate
    FixedFrequencyScale
    Special fixed frequency scale used by LFO nodes to hold their modulating data algorithm
    FxAudioAlgorithm
    Base class for Fx algorithms.
    GenAudioAlgorithm
    Base class for Gen algorithms.
    Properties
    Each algorithm that is assigned to a DraggableNode holds an instance of this class, which encapsulates necessary parameters for the algorithm.
    Property
    Data structure for one property of a DraggableNode's AudioAlgorithm.
    Scale
    This class represents the musical scale corresponding to a GenNode.
